Package problem01.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IInitializeTodoList
    Interface describing the public functionality of an InitializeTodoList object, comprising of the ability to generate a List of Todos from a provided Map, storing relevant information.
    IReadCSV
    Interface describing the public functionality of a ReadCSV object, comprising of the ability to store contents of a csv file, row by row.
    IValidateInput
    Interface describing the public functionality of a ValidateInput object, comprising of the ability to check various CLI arguments for validity.
    IWriteCSV
    Interface describing the public functionality of a WriteCSV object, comprising of the ability to write store To-do information to a csv file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckNullUtils
    Class which determines whether arguments utilized within function calls can be classified as null.
    InitializeTodoList
    Class which generates a To-do list, based on a provided Map, retaining all information to be stored within a To-do object.
    ReadCSV
    Class which reads and stored To-do information from a provided .csv file.
    ValidateInput
    Class utilized to validate CLI arguments, ensuring their correctness.
    WriteCSV
    Class which writes all stored To-do information within a provided .csv file.
